extends _layout.pug
block content
  .container
    h1 Free Code Camp
    h2.subheading Image Search Abstraction Layer
    p Image search is a full stack JavaScript app built for #[a(href='https://www.freecodecamp.com/challenges/image-search-abstraction-layer', target='_blank') Free Code Camp].
    blockquote
      p User stories:
      ul
        li I can get the image URLs, alt text and page urls for a set of images relating to a given search string.
        li I can paginate through the responses by adding a ?offset=2 parameter to the URL.
        li I can get a list of the most recently submitted search strings.
    .live
      h2 Live Example
      p By clicking in the input field below, you can see the recent searches. If you click on any of them, it loads the images immediately. Of course, you can also search by typing in the field and hitting enter.
      form(autocomplete='off')
        input#search(placeholder='Type something and hit Enter...')
        ul#recent.recent
      #results.results
  script(src='app.js')
